description: The manager seeks to achieve the fund's investment objective by investing in common stocks and other equity securities of companies of all sizes. The manager maintains a portfolio of investments consisting primarily of common stocks. The fund may also invest in other equity securities, such as preferred stocks, rights, or warrants. It may have significant exposure to the information technology sector. The fund invests in a broad group of companies, including many that are in their early stages of development. It is non-diversified.
name: Jacob Forward ETF
